data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom haven nestled conveniently near Foxbank Elementary and Foxbank Plantation shopping center. This stunning home boasts an array of desirable features, including granite countertops, a cozy fireplace, and LVP flooring. Step outside to the inviting screened patio and explore the expansive fenced yard, offering ample space for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. Upstairs, discover a versatile loft area perfect for various lifestyle needs. The owner's suite is a true retreat, complete with a soothing garden tub and shower combo, providing the ultimate relaxation experience. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with a convenient Jack&Jill bathroom to facilitate seamless living. Resort style pool, private lake,dog park etc
